body_text.text:
To test whether CymMV-M2 can replicate in N. benthamiana, protoplasts were inoculated with transcripts from pCymMV-M1, pCymMV-M2, pCymMV-M1-GFP and pCymMV-M2-GFP. Illumination of GFP was observed from pCymMV-M1-GFP and pCymMV-M2-GFP infected protoplasts at 14 h post-inoculation (Fig. 2
). Northern blot hybridization also indicated that pCymMV-M1 and pCymMV-M2 replicated in N. benthamiana protoplasts (Fig. 3
I).
